The Proposal


The FAA is considering an amendment to part 71 of the Federal Aviation Regulations (14 CFR part 71) to modify controlled
airspace in the vicinity of Morgantown, WV, to reflect the proposed cancellation of the NDB or GPS Runway 18 SIAP, the
