NPRM. Any person who wishes to speak should notify Daphen&eacute; Floyd at (202) 366-1640. Please estimate
the time that will be needed to speak. RSPA reserves the right to limit the time of each speaker, if necessary, to ensure
that everyone who requests an opportunity to speak is given one. Individuals that are not scheduled to comment will
have an opportunity to comment only after approval of the meeting officer.

